      <section eId="sec_37_0105">
        <num>37-0105</num>
        <heading>Rules and regulations</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_37_0105__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_37_0105__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of subdivision one of section 37-0103 of this\nchapter are based to furnish to the department for the public record any\ninformation regarding such substances which the said user may have, and\nthe nature and extent of research performed by said user concerning the\neffects of such substances on human health and the environment. Prior to\npromulgation of rules and regulations hereunder, public hearings shall\nbe held upon notice in two newspapers in the locality of said public\nhearings, at least two times per week in each of three successive weeks.\nSuch hearings shall be conducted not less than sixty</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_37_0105__subsec_b__subsec_60">
            <num>(60)</num>
            <content>
              <p>days following\nthe date of last publication.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
      </section>
